-- Petrobras Discovers Oil in Onshore Sao Mateus Leste Well in Espirito Santo
-- Laura Price
-- 2010-07-01T07:56:08Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-01/petrobras-discovers-oil-in-onshore-sao-mateus-leste-well-in-espirito-santo.html

          
          
             Petroleo Brasileiro SA , Brazil’s
state-controlled oil company, discovered oil in an onshore well
of the Sao Mateus Leste block in the country’s  Espirito Santo
Basin .  
 The  3BRSA838ES  well hasn’t yet been declared commercially
viable. Petrobras, as the Rio de Janeiro-based company is known,
 reported the discovery  on the website of Brazil’s National
Petroleum Agency.  
